{"per_page":10,"total":15,"current":14,"data":[{"title":"Mybatis报错org.mybatis.spring.MyBatisSystemException","date":"2018-04-26T00:01:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/54","tags":["error_info","flec","getter","named","nested"],"categories":["Mybatis"]},{"title":"这大概只能是死宅才会体会的快乐吧","date":"2018-04-24T04:20:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/48","categories":["Life"]},{"title":"在本地用navicat链接不上阿里云ECS服务器上的数据库问题解决","date":"2018-04-22T23:16:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"问题原因：mysql权限问题\">问题原因：mysql权限问题<a href=\"post/44#问题原因：mysql权限问题\"></a></h1><h1 id=\"解决方法-1：\">解决方法 1：<a href=\"post/44#解决方法-1：\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">//设置root用户通过123456密码可以从任何主机连接到mysql服务器</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt;GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO &apos;username&apos;@&apos;%&apos; IDENTIFIED BY &apos;password&apos; WITH GRANT OPTION;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec)  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">//刷新mysql权限表</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt;FLUSH PRIVILEGES;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.00 sec) </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//查询用户表</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysql&gt; select host,user from user;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>ALL PRIVILEGES –所有的权限，当然这里也可以写增删查改update delete insert select</li>\n<li><em>.</em>  – 指的是所有数据库的权限，‘<em>数据库.表’</em></li>\n</ul>","link":"post/44","tags":["grant","mysql","privileges","rows","指定","数据库","服务器","权限","访问"],"categories":["DataBase","Liunx"]},{"title":"CentSO 7.4 下安装jdk1.8、mysql、php服务","date":"2018-04-22T22:51:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-安装jdk1-8\">1.安装jdk1.8<a href=\"post/43#1-安装jdk1-8\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\">1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1.1 安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk<a href=\"post/43#1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk1-1-安装之前先检查一下系统有没有自带open-jdk\"></a></h2><p>命令：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep java</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep jdk</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa |grep gcj</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>如果没有输入信息表示没有安装。<br>如果安装可以使用如果安装可以使用<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa | grep java | xargs rpm -e --nodeps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>批量卸载所有带有Java的文件  这句命令的关键字是java</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-2-检索包含java的列表\">1.2 检索包含java的列表<a href=\"post/43#1-2-检索包含java的列表\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum list java*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/43","tags":["1.8.0","gcj","grep","java","javarpm","jdkrpm","mysql","open-jdk","php","php-fpm","service","yum","命令","安装","文件","系统"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"阿里云服务器下(centOS)中安装ftp","date":"2018-04-20T03:17:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-安装常用工具和依赖库\">1.安装常用工具和依赖库<a href=\"post/40#1-安装常用工具和依赖库\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo yum install wget axel unzip gcc bison git autoconf nfs-utils pcre-devel zlib-devel bzip2-devel cmake gcc-c++ ncurses-devel perl-Data-Dumper libicu-devel libquadmath-devel python-devel libxml2-devel openssl-devel libcurl-devel libpng-devel freetype-devel freetype-devel gd-devel libmcrypt-devel libxslt-devel libevent-devel systemd-devel make gtk+-devel openssl keyutils patch perl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"2-获取PHP\">2.获取PHP<a href=\"post/40#2-获取PHP\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget http://cn2.php.net/distributions/php-7.1.9.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/40","tags":["ftp","ftpservice","permanent","systemctl","tcp","yes","zone","命令","客户端","文件","服务器","端口"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"centOS 用rpm查看已经安装的程序","date":"2018-04-20T02:56:00.000Z","excerpt":"<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">rpm -qa | grep xxxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-a：查询所有套件；</span><br><span class=\"line\">-q：使用询问模式，当遇到任何问题时，rpm指令会先询问用户；</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"所有参数：\">所有参数：<a href=\"post/38#所有参数：\"></a></h1>","link":"post/38","tags":["grep","p","参数","套件","指令","指定","文件"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"centOS 7 下firewalld防火墙基本命令的使用","date":"2018-04-19T01:56:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-firewalld-的基本使用\">1.firewalld 的基本使用<a href=\"post/35#1-firewalld-的基本使用\"></a></h1><p>一下命令是在root用户下使用，如果不是请加sudo<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">启动：systemctl start firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">状态：systemctl status firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">关闭：systemctl stop firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">暂停：systemctl disable firewalld</span><br><span class=\"line\">重启:systemctl restart firewalld</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/35","tags":["firewalld","permanent","systemctl","tcp","zone","命令"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":" linux （centos 7）ps命令查看应用程序进程号、端口","date":"2018-04-19T00:55:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"1-查看xxx进程对应的进程号\">1.查看xxx进程对应的进程号<a href=\"post/34#1-查看xxx进程对应的进程号\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ps aux | grep xxx</span><br><span class=\"line\">ps -ef | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h2 id=\"1-1-ps-aux、ps-aux、ps-ef之间的区别\">1.1 ps aux、ps -aux、ps -ef之间的区别<a href=\"post/34#1-1-ps-aux、ps-aux、ps-ef之间的区别\"></a></h2><p>Linux中的ps命令是Process Status的缩写。ps命令用来列出系统中当前运行的那些进程。ps命令列出的是当前那些进程的快照，就是执行ps命令的那个时刻的那些进程，如果想要动态的显示进程信息，就可以使用top命令。<br>具体参数可以参考man ps或<br><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/peida/archive/2012/12/19/2824418.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.cnblogs.com/peida/archive/2012/12/19/2824418.html</a><br></p>","link":"post/34","tags":["aux","grep","命令","显示","进程"],"categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"ssm框架中dao层如何调用数据库中数据spring配置——个人小总结","date":"2018-04-13T01:39:00.000Z","excerpt":"<ol>\n<li>propertyConfigurer读取dbconfig数据库连接信息，通过<code>org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer</code> 将dbcongfig的信息返回给<code>阿里 druid数据库连接池</code><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;bean id=&quot;propertyConfigurer&quot; class=&quot;org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;property name=&quot;locations&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;list&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;value&gt;/WEB-INF/classes/dbconfig.properties&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/list&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/bean&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>","link":"post/30","tags":["dao","daosupport","obj","str","数据库"],"categories":["Spring"]},{"title":"linux设置开机启动 systemctl enable","date":"2018-04-09T03:13:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"是超级用户权限下\">是超级用户权限下<a href=\"post/25#是超级用户权限下\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable //这句话的意思就是将那个服务设置开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable httpd //设置开机启动httpd服务</span><br><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable php-fpm //设置php开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","link":"post/25","tags":["enable","php","php-fpm","systemctl","开机"],"categories":["Liunx"]}]}